# OpenClaw Memory Repository
# Git-synced persistent memory for AI assistant

## Temporary files
*.tmp
*.log
*.swp
*~

## Cache directories
.cache/
qmd/
**/node_modules/

## Sensitive information (NEVER commit these)
.env
.env.local
*.key
*.pem
secrets/
credentials/

## Session state (local only)
.openclaw/workspace-state.json
.openclaw/sessions/

## Build artifacts
dist/
build/

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

## Keep memory files (explicitly included)
!MEMORY.md
!memory/
!SOUL.md
!USER.md
!IDENTITY.md
!AGENTS.md
!TOOLS.md
!HEARTBEAT.md
